				<div class="post clearfix">
					<h1 class="title">Desserts to Love!</h1>
											<p class="post-meta">Posted  by <a href="http://www.bellalimento.com/author/paula/" title="Posts by Paula">Paula</a> in <a href="http://www.bellalimento.com/category/recipes/" title="View all posts in All Recipes" rel="category tag">All Recipes</a>, <a href="http://www.bellalimento.com/category/recipes/desserts/" title="View all posts in Desserts" rel="category tag">Desserts</a> | <a href="http://www.bellalimento.com/2011/02/11/desserts-to-love/#comments" title="Comment on Desserts to Love!">17 comments</a></p>
																				
								
					<p><span class="rdetector_placeholder_before"></span><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3909" title="nutellalava5_wm" src="http://www.bellalimento.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/02/nutellalava5_wm.jpg" alt="" width="558" height="414" /></p>
<p>Valentine&#8217;s Day is upon us. In just a few short days people will be celebrating LOVE all over the world. &lt;3 &lt;3 &lt;3. In Italy it&#8217;s called San Valentino, which as with everything else sounds so much bettter in Italian ; ) I say we all eat cake&#8230;<a href="http://www.bellalimento.com/2010/02/04/chocolate-nutella-molten-lava-cake/"  target="_self"> Chocolate Nutella Molten Lava Cake</a> to be exact; ) Sinfully decadent and super SEXY!Â  <span id="more-8365"></span><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-3999" title="pannacotta3_wm" src="http://www.bellalimento.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/02/pannacotta3_wm.jpg" alt="" width="558" height="414" /></p>
<p>Or if Molten Lava Cakes aren&#8217;t your thing..How about<a href="http://www.bellalimento.com/2010/02/11/panna-cotta/"  target="_self"> Panna Cotta</a> ; ) It&#8217;s creamy, luscious and best part, it&#8217;s something you can whip up in just ten minutes and then pop into the fridge to set up! Go ahead and get creative with the flavors. You can add just about any flavor to Panna Cotta. I&#8217;ve made <a href="http://www.bellalimento.com/2010/07/07/panna-cotta-al-limoncello-limoncello-panna-cotta/"  target="_self">Limoncello Panna Cotta</a>, <a href="http://www.bellalimento.com/2010/05/12/panna-cotta-alla-nutella-nutella-panna-cotta/"  target="_self">Nutella Panna Cotta</a>, and<a href="http://www.bellalimento.com/2010/11/10/panna-cotta-alla-melagrana-pomegranate-panna-cotta/"  target="_self"> Pomegranate Panna Cotta. </a></p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-2391" title="cremebrulee5_wm" src="http://www.bellalimento.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/10/cremebrulee5_wm.jpg" alt="" width="558" height="414" /></p>
<p>Or perhaps you like wielding a kitchen torch! Who doesn&#8217;t love a kitchen torch ; ) Well, then it&#8217;s <a href="http://www.bellalimento.com/2009/10/01/the-nutella-challenge-nutella-creme-brulee/"  target="_self">Nutella Creme Brulee&#8217;</a> for you!</p>
<p>And if you need any other sinfully scrumptious suggestions for your sweet tooth, pop on over to <a href="http://www.bellanutella.com" onclick="javascript:_gaq.push(['_trackEvent','outbound-article','www.bellanutella.com']);" target="_blank">bella nutella! </a></p>
<p>Baci e Buon San Valentino!</p>
<p><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-6221" title="signature2010" src="http://www.bellalimento.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/08/signature2010.png" alt="" width="250" height="80" />
